description: Redevelopment by the erection of a 43 storey residential tower, comprising 212 residential units, with ground floor Class A1/A2/A3/A4/A5 units, ancillary basement parking, public viewing gallery, highway works, new vehicular and pedestrian accesses, new bridge and associated works to Paddington Basin, closure of public highway, highway improvements and associated hard and soft landscaping (Building A).
